 couldn't convince the judge

00:42.710 --> 00:44.877
that your new mixed-use
 facility would cause

00:44.879 --> 00:46.578
any negative impact at all.

00:46.580 --> 00:48.147
That's amazing.

00:48.149 --> 00:50.783
- So I need you
 to look at these contracts

00:50.785 --> 00:51.917
and get right back to me.

00:51.919 --> 00:53.452
- Will do.

00:53.454 --> 00:54.553
- Now, I'll be staying in
 the city for the holidays.

00:54.555 --> 00:56.055
- Uh huh.

00:56.057 --> 00:58.524
- So I'll be available any
 time to consult on this

00:58.526 --> 01:00.292
- Do you
 know that it's Christmas?

01:00.294 --> 01:03.495
- Yes, I know it's Christmas,
 but this is a very big deal,

01:03.497 --> 01:05.263
and I wanna make
  it happen for you.

01:05.266 --> 01:06.231
- Got it.

01:06.233 --> 01:07.666
- I will do whatever it takes.

01:07.668 --> 01:08.600
- Thank you.

01:08.602 --> 01:09.435
Merry Christmas to you.

01:09.437 --> 01:10.502
- You're welcome.

01:10.504 --> 01:12.771
Merry Christmas to you, too.

01:12.773 --> 01:14.673
- Making people's
 dreams come true again?

01:14.675 --> 01:15.974
- It's what I do.

01:18.579 --> 01:19.411
Karen.

01:19.413 --> 01:20.846
- Yeah.

01:20.848 --> 01:22.414
- I need to reschedule my
tomorrow with the seaport people

01:22.416 --> 01:24.383
from 10:30 to 11:30 if possible.

01:24.385 --> 01:25.217
- Okay.

01:26.654 --> 01:28.587
- And I also need you see
 if you can change that lunch

01:28.589 --> 01:31.356
with Ben Harrington and his
 attorney to drinks instead.

01:31.358 --> 01:33.025
Let's say 5:30.

01:33.027 --> 01:35.094
No, let's make it 5:15.

01:35.096 --> 01:36.962
I'll show up at 5:30 so
 they can worry a bit.

01:38.199 --> 01:40.232
- 10:30 to
 11:30, lunch to drinks,

01:40.234 --> 01:42.334
make 'em worry, got it.

01:42.336 --> 01:44.937
The famous Lucy
  Toomey power play.

01:44.939 --> 01:47.172
- I'm sure I have no idea
 what you're talking about.

01:47.174 --> 01:49.908
- Oh, wait.

01:49.910 --> 01:54.413
The courier dropped this
 at the front desk for you.

01:54.415 --> 01:55.547
- Yes!

01:55.549 --> 01:57.316
- What is it?

01:57.318 --> 01:59.384
- My tickets to the
 Nutcracker at Lincoln Center.

01:59.386 --> 02:01.019
- Oh, nice.

02:01.021 --> 02:02.821
Who's the lucky guy?

02:02.823 --> 02:04.890
- Actually it's my sister.

02:04.892 --> 02:06.992
Alice lives back
  where we grew up

02:06.994 --> 02:08.594
in Nilson's Bay, in Wisconsin.

02:08.596 --> 02:09.595
- Huh, let me guess.

02:09.597 --> 02:11.330
She's older, right?

02:11.332 --> 02:12.564
- How do you know that?

02:12.566 --> 02:14.700
- Ha, you totally have
 little sister syndrome.

02:14.702 --> 02:15.868
- What?

02:15.870 --> 02:17.369
- Luce, you're a
  complete overachiever.

02:17.371 --> 02:19.471
You knock yourself out on
 every single case you take.

02:20.708 --> 02:23.075
Alice must have been
  a tough act to follow.

02:23.077 --> 02:24.643
- Just because she
  got a full scholarship

02:24.645 --> 02:27.112
to veterinary college,
 and was first chair violin

02:27.114 --> 02:28.947
in school orchestra,
  and Homecoming Queen?

02:28.949 --> 02:32.017
- Oh, see what I mean?

02:32.019 --> 02:34.887
Hey, maybe we can hit up some
 clubs when she's in town.

02:34.889 --> 02:36.121
You know, show her
  how New Yorkers like

02:36.123 --> 02:37.389
to party at Christmas.

02:37.391 --> 02:39.024
- Oh, that's really
  sweet of you, Karen.

02:39.026 --> 02:42.594
Uh, the thing is, uh,
 Alice has some challenges.

02:42.596 --> 02:44.129
- Okay.

02:44.131 --> 02:47.199
- Uh, she was in a car accident
when she was in college,

02:47.201 --> 02:49.768
and she got a pretty
  bad head injury.

02:51.005 --> 02:52.538
- Lucy, I'm so sorry.

02:52.540 --> 02:53.438
I didn't know.

02:54.375 --> 02:55.607
- She does pretty well, though.

02:55.609 --> 02:57.442
And she loves the Nutcracker.

02:57.444 --> 02:59.444
She comes here to see it
 with me every Christmas.

02:59.446 --> 03:02.848
- Well, I can't
  wait to meet her.

03:02.850 --> 03:04.049
Oh my goodness.

03:04.051 --> 03:05.584
Okay, uh, the office
 party is in three hours,

03:05.586 --> 03:09.087
and I haven't done my hair,
 so, see see ya tonight?

03:09.089 --> 03:09.788
- Yeah.

