  couldn't help myself.

43:04.182 --> 43:06.549
I snuck one of those
  Christmas cookies,

43:06.551 --> 43:07.984
and they are umm.

43:12.424 --> 43:16.025
- Lucy, have you
  ever quilted before?

43:16.027 --> 43:16.859
- Me?

