  a button on a shirt.

43:20.498 --> 43:21.831
- Oh, we've always
  had four people

43:21.833 --> 43:23.633
in our quilting group, Lucy.

43:23.635 --> 43:25.835
With Alice gone, it
  just, it feels...

43:25.837 --> 43:27.403
- It feels like
  someone's missing.

43:27.405 --> 43:28.972
- Oh, no, no, no, no, no.

43:28.974 --> 43:31.574
- It would mean a lot
  if you would help us.

43:31.576 --> 43:33.076
- I am sorry.

43:33.078 --> 43:35.678
I would really love to help,
 but I don't know anything

43:35.680 --> 43:36.913
about making a quilt.

43:36.915 --> 43:38.448
- Oh, Rinda taught
  me in like an hour.

43:38.450 --> 43:39.282
- I mean, yeah.

43:39.284 --> 43:40.950
- It's no problem, Lucy.

43:40.952 --> 43:42.018
Don't worry about it.

43:42.020 --> 43:44.220
We'll be okay on our own.

43:44.222 --> 43:47.023
I mean, no one is gonna
 judge you, just because

43:47.025 --> 43:49.959
you don't wanna help us
 finish this very special quilt

43:49.961 --> 43:51.894
that Alice helped make.

