I saw him eyeing
  them all night long.

47:18.937 --> 47:20.436
- I will, promise.

47:21.272 --> 47:22.171
- Good night.

47:22.173 --> 47:23.840
- Good night.

47:25.009 --> 47:26.843
Thank you for tonight.

47:27.979 --> 47:29.779
I guess I really needed this.

47:29.781 --> 47:32.582
- We had a lotta nights
 like this with Alice.

47:32.584 --> 47:34.116
A lotta fun.

47:34.118 --> 47:37.119
She always said she wished
 you could have been here.

47:37.121 --> 47:37.954
Bye, Lucy.

47:40.892 --> 47:42.458
- Goodnight.

48:40.084 --> 48:45.087
- I knew Alice took art
classes as part of her therapy,

48:45.223 --> 48:47.890
but I didn't know she
  was this artistic.

48:47.892 --> 48:49.492
Who do you think this is?

48:49.494 --> 48:51.360
- Well, they're all self
 portraits, aren't they?

48:51.362 --> 48:53.195
- I don't think so.

48:53.197 --> 48:55.932
The hair's different, and
 there's something in the eyes.

48:55.934 --> 48:56.866
- Uncle Barney,

48:56.868 --> 48:57.700
- Yeah.

48:58.770 --> 49:01.137
- Do you know
  somebody named Maeve?

49:01.139 --> 49:03.239
- Maeve, Maeve, no.

49:03.241 --> 49:04.273
Can't say that I do.

49:04.275 --> 49:05.408
Why?

49:05.410 --> 49:07.877
- I found some beautiful
 Christmas quilts

49:07.879 --> 49:10.212
in a trunk upstairs.

49:10.214 --> 49:12.615
