 tag with the name Maeve

49:12.617 --> 49:14.083
embroidered on them.

49:14.085 --> 49:15.685
I thought maybe Alice had
 made them for somebody

49:15.687 --> 49:16.686
in the family?

49:16.688 --> 49:18.220
- Name doesn't ring a bell.

49:18.222 --> 49:22.725
But like I told you, a
 lot of people knew Alice.

49:22.727 --> 49:25.061
What are your plans
  for Christmas?

49:25.063 --> 49:26.662
- Actually, I wasn't
  gonna make any.

49:26.664 --> 49:29.498
I thought I'd just stay
 in and get some work done.

49:29.500 --> 49:31.600
- Well that's ridiculous.

49:31.602 --> 49:33.836
Whatta you say, I'll put
 together a little dinner

49:33.838 --> 49:34.737
for the both of us?

49:34.739 --> 49:35.638
Which would you like?

49:35.640 --> 49:36.973
Ham or Turkey?

49:36.975 --> 49:37.907
- No, really.

49:37.909 --> 49:41.277
- I'll put in an order for both.

49:41.279 --> 49:42.979
That's a nice tree.

49:42.981 --> 49:44.547
Where'd it come from?

49:44.549 --> 49:46.382
- Peter Swinson
  bought it for Alice?

49:46.384 --> 49:49.151
- Well, now, I haven't
 heard you say that name

49:49.153 --> 49:50.386
in a long time.

49:52.223 --> 49:57.226
Whatta you say we invite him
 over for Christmas dinner?

49:58.696 --> 50:00.162
It's be nice to see you two
 getting back together again.

50:00.164 --> 50:03.933
- We're not getting back
 together again, Uncle Barney.

50:03.935 --> 50:06.268
He just helped with the tree.

50:06.270 --> 50:08.337
- Okay, whatever you say.

50:11.442 --> 50:14.043
You know he was Alice's lawyer.

50:15.179 --> 50:17.113
Did you ask him about
  this Maeve person?

50:17.115 --> 50:19.482
- He said he didn't
 know anything about it.

50:19.484 --> 50:20.783
- It's a small town.

50:20.785 --> 50:23.386
Maybe he can help you find her.

50:26.457 --> 50:28.524
- Mr. Swinson is not in
 the office right now,

50:28.526 --> 50:29.959
may I take a message?

50:29.961 --> 50:32.028
- Hi, Carla, it's Lucy Toomey.

50:32.030 --> 50:34.530
I tried him on his cell,
 but I couldn't reach him.

50:34.532 --> 50:38.968
- Hi, Lucy, yeah, yeah, that's
 because he's on the ice.

50:38.970 --> 50:40.836
- Oh, he's at the rink?

50:40.838 --> 50:43.439
- Oh, no, not that ice.

50:43.441 --> 50:44.840
The blue ice.

50:44.842 --> 50:45.875
He's fishin'.

50:49.847 --> 50:53.015
Now you cannot miss
  Mr. Swinson's hut.

50:54.652 --> 50:56.919
Look for all the Christmas.

51:26.451 --> 51:27.249
- Peter!

51:32.056 --> 51:34.557
- Lucy, what are you doin' here?

51:34.559 --> 51:35.591
- You know I was
 in the neighborhood,

51:35.593 --> 51:36.625
so I thought I'd stop by.

51:37.462 --> 51:38.727
- What?

51:38.729 --> 51:39.562
- It's cold.

51:39.564 --> 51:40.796
- Hey, hey.

51:40.798 --> 51:44.233
- Oh, I love what you've
 done with the place.

51:44.235 --> 51:45.067
- Thanks.

51:45.069 --> 51:46.402
Be careful there.

51:46.404 --> 51:47.236
- Oh.

51:47.238 --> 51:48.370
- Sorry for the mess.

51:48.372 --> 51:49.672
I don't get any guests.

51:49.674 --> 51:51.273
I think yoghbe the first.

51:51.275 --> 51:52.274
Have a seat.

51:55.580 --> 51:56.412
- Thanks

51:57.582 --> 51:58.581
How's the fishing?

51:58.583 --> 51:59.515
- Don't ask.

51:59.517 --> 52:01.250
I've changed the lures twice.

52:01.252 --> 52:02.751
But I think they're on to me.

52:02.753 --> 52:06.555
May I offer you a specialty
 of the house, hot apple cider?

52:06.557 --> 52:08.057
- Yes, I would like that.

52:08.059 --> 52:09.325
Thank you.

52:09.327 --> 52:12.828
- So what brings you
  all the way out here?

52:12.830 --> 52:14.830
- You remember that quilt
 with the name Maeve on it?

52:16.000 --> 52:17.166
- Uh, huh.

52:17.168 --> 52:19.602
- I found a trunk-full
  in Alice's room,

52:19.604 --> 52:21.604
all with the same
  name on the tags.

52:21.606 --> 52:24.673
Are you sure Alice
  didn't mention her?

52:24.675 --> 52:27.443
- Not that I can tell you.

52:27.445 --> 52:31.547
- Well I've been looking
 for her on the internet,

52:33.251 --> 52:34.783
but I haven't found anything.

52:34.785 --> 52:36.452
I thought maybe
  you could help me.

52:36.454 --> 52:37.386
Ask around?

52:38.356 --> 52:40.289
Check out the town records?

52:40.291 --> 52:41.891
- Yeah, without a last
  name, I'm not sure

52:41.893 --> 52:43.259
how far we'd get.

52:45.897 --> 52:49.732
Sounds like it's really
 important to you, isn't it?

52:49.734 --> 52:51.834
- In a way, yes.

52:51.836 --> 52:55.437
I feel like I wanna do
  something for Alice.

52:55.439 --> 52:59.308
- You came here for Christmas,
 maybe that's enough.

53:00.378 --> 53:01.377
Oh, yes!
